OL,3,CFormer Labour minister and crossbench
OL,4,Cpeer Frank Field dies, aged 81
OL,6,FFormer Labour minister and crossbench
OL,7,Fpeer Frank Field has died aged 81, his
OL,8,Ffamily has announced.
OL,10,FLord Field of Birkenhead died in a
OL,11,FLondon care home on Tuesday night, 23
OL,12,FApril, following a period of illness,
OL,13,Fand is survived by two brothers.
OL,15,FHe revealed he was terminally ill in
OL,16,FOctober 2021 and had spent time in a
OL,17,Fhospice when a statement from him was
OL,18,Fread out in the House of Lords calling
OL,19,Ffor laws on assisted dying to be
OL,20,Frelaxed.
