OL,6,FA statement from Lord Field of
OL,7,FBirkenhead's family, issued by his
OL,8,FParliamentary office, said: "Frank
OL,9,FField (Rt Hon Lord Field of
OL,10,FBirkenhead, CH) has died at the age of
OL,11,F81 following a period of illness.
OL,13,F"Frank was director of the Child
OL,14,FPoverty Action Group between 1969 and
OL,15,F1979, and the Member of Parliament for
OL,16,FBirkenhead between 1979 and 2019.
