OL,6,F"Frank was principled, courageous, and
OL,7,Findependent-minded. He cared about the
OL,8,Fpeople he served, thought deeply about
OL,9,Fthe issues he championed, and worked
OL,10,Fentirely for the good of the people of
OL,11,FBirkenhead as their MP for 40 years.
OL,12,FHis honour and integrity were well
OL,13,Fknown and admired.
OL,15,F"On behalf of the Labour Party, my
OL,16,Fthoughts are with his family."
OL,18,FThe Speaker of the House of Commons
OL,19,Fand Chorley MP Sir Lindsay Hoyle also
OL,20,Fpaid tribute to Lord Field.
