OL,6,FIn a statement he said:
OL,8,F"As a former colleague, I watched in
OL,9,Fadmiration as Frank Field navigated a
OL,10,Fcareer as a formidable MP, and as a
OL,11,Fminister, tasked with 'thinking the
OL,12,Funthinkable' on social care.
OL,14,F"He was neither cowed by the
OL,15,Festablishment or whips - which made
OL,16,Fhis campaigns against hunger and food
OL,17,Fpoverty, for climate change and for
OL,18,Fthe church, even more effective.
